{
  "body": "## The problem\r\n\r\nThe GitHub API [returns only traffic stats for the last 14 days](https://developer.github.com/v3/repos/traffic/#views). It would be interesting to check longer-term terms.\r\n\r\n## Suggestions\r\n\r\nIt's a single query and it can be done every 7 days or so from some site, stored in JSON form and processed somehow. A cron job would probably do the trick.",
